dct_description_sm: 2 maps on 1 sheet, State Forests and The Lincoln Hills. Lincoln Hills map (1:690,000) shows Lincoln Heritage Trail, various Lincoln-related sites and other natural and cultural resources in Harrison, Crawford, Perry, and Spencer counties along the southern border of Indiana.    Detached from: An atlas of Indiana / by Robert C. Kingsbury , with contributions from John M. Hollingsworth and others. Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]. Page 84.
Imprint: Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]
Scale: Approximately 1:1,600,000; Dimensions: each 13 x 18 cm, on sheet 28 x 21 cm
dct_spatial_sm: Indiana--Lincoln Hills Resource Conservation and Development Project Area
